  "summary": "Malicious code in solanarpclampweb3 (npm)",
  "details": "Solanarpclampweb3 exports a function designed to accept a wallet private key as an argument and exfiltrate it to a Telegram bot. The function constructs a POST request to api[.]telegram[.]org using a hardcoded bot token, sending the private key as a text message to a hardcoded Telegram chat ID. The package name mimics a Solana/Web3 RPC utility to trick users into importing it and passing their private key, which is then exfiltrated via Telegram's API.",
